---
title: Easy Roast Vegetable Bianca Pizza with Rocket Salad
description: Pizza bianca or "white pizza" in Italian, refers to pizza with no tomato sauce. Sometimes topped with a combination of cheeses
and a few simple ingredients, we think it's one of the best pizzas you'll ever try. You'll never even miss the tomato sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-vegetable-bianca-pizza-e9abea41.jpg
